ong-term sustainability!\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Refined `BCGOST3410PublicKeyTest` to make the serialization coverage more explicit for the active class.\n\nChanges in:\n\n`tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk18on/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk18on/BCGOST3410PublicKeyTest.java`\n\nUpdates:\n- Test helpers now use the concrete `BCGOST3410PublicKey` type instead of only the `GOST3410PublicKey` interface.\n- Added explicit tracking for both serialization branches:\n  - named GOST parameter OID branch\n  - explicit GOST parameter object branch\n- `TrackingObjectInputStream` now verifies the exact objects read during deserialization, strengthening coverage of `BCGOST3410PublicKey.readObject(...)`.\n- `TrackingObjectOutputStream` continues verifying objects written by `BCGOST3410PublicKey.writeObject(...)`.\n\nI did not run the Gradle test command locally, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_03dab8d6da908998016a25e3a31e408197affedca897d6429f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2456, "output": 721, "cacheRead": 36864, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 40041, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1780867987964, "responseId": "resp_03dab8d6da908998016a25e3948e288197896b8882629b4695"}, "toolResults": []}
